{"tid":570660,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［急］拾遺不報有冇得打？","createTime":"2018-02-24T01:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T03:58:52.000Z","uid":10608,"like":0,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"83dc06de3b0dc6b258b659f54638d82a9098ec96","tid":570660,"uid":10608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:15:30.000Z","msg":"我係琴日拾到部iPhone 5s，之後今日係先達度放機，<br />\n點知報警果間鋪職員一開始問我：4200放唔放。<br />\n我話：唔放，俾番部手機黎。<br />\n佢唔肯，就扣住左部5s，<br />\n佢話：咁你話部電話係拾既，就打電話報警，撗掂我有大把時候同你慢慢玩。<br />\n佢打左兩次，係佢打第二次既時候，<br />\n我話：俾番部電話我，我趕住番工。<br />\n佢就話：呢嫁二千就放俾你。<br />\n最後差人黎到，搵我番去落口供<br />\n<br />\n我有同警察講番呢件事，但佢地冇寫係口供度，正係寫話我係先達放機之後俾職員知道我係拾就打電話報警。<br />\n懇求各位可以幫幫我俾少少意見"},{"pid":"926917cf762c22efdeed952cdfe918f113eb0bec","tid":570660,"uid":64345,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:16:44.000Z","msg":"偷野仲學人講價"},{"pid":"ce4858f53eff09cbb976c9d224887f8b171710d9","tid":570660,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7f2a4f188ecc9843fdcfb945945560b8537b5a","tid":570660,"uid":11049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:17:59.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"d931e96c470aef6dd878397c21fb56cc9cafd9f3","tid":570660,"uid":398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:18:18.000Z","msg":"當然要打！"},{"pid":"0794c5e1e5961d7c8d50e76c86f29bd4a6741646","tid":570660,"uid":68040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:18:40.000Z","msg":"貪字得個貧呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353fb0afde05f41566acbf76d691f35d1dd9dd13","tid":570660,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T01:19:49.000Z","msg":"又一條假腸"},{"pid":"c8d53f6e870053aafbe191ea0ead96fbc30af659","tid":570660,"uid":10608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d931e96c470aef6dd878397c21fb56cc9cafd9f3","t